#: activities/chess/ActivityInfo.qml:24
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid ""
"In this activity you discover the chess game by playing against the "
"computer. It displays the possible target positions for any selected piece "
"which helps the children understand how pieces moves. At first level the "
"computer is fully random to give more chances to the children. As level "
"increases, the computer plays better. You can use the arrow buttons to "
"manually select the difficulty level.\n"
"\n"
"You can achieve a mate sooner if you follow these simple rules:\n"
"    Trying to drive your opponent's king in the corner.\n"
"<b>Explanation</b>: this way your opponent's king would have only 3 "
"directions to move instead of 8 from a better position.\n"
"    'Making a trap'. Use your pawns as baits.\n"
"<b>Explanation</b>: this way you can lure your opponent out of his 'comfort "
"zone'.\n"
"    Be patient enough.\n"
"<b>Explanation</b>: don't rush too quick, be patient. Let yourself think a "
"little bit and try to predict your opponent's future moves, so that you can "
"catch him or secure your pieces from his attacks."
msgstr ""
"Bu ΟßalΡ±≈ümada siz kompyuter…ô qar≈üΡ± oynamaq qaydalarΡ±nΡ± ΟΕyr…ôn…ôc…ôksiniz. "
"Gedi≈ül…ôrin i≈üΡ±qlanmasΡ± say…ôsind…ô hansΡ± gedi≈üin edildiyini bil…ôc…ôksiniz. "
"Kompyuter birinci s…ôviyy…ôd…ô gedi≈üini t…ôsadΟΦfi olaraq seΟßir v…ô oynamaq Οßox "
"asandΡ±r. S…ôviyy…ô artdΡ±qca kompyuter daha gΟΦclΟΦ oynamaΡüa ba≈ülayΡ±r. Siz 0x "
"dΟΦym…ôl…ôrind…ôn istifad…ô ed…ôr…ôk Οß…ôtinlik s…ôviyy…ôsini …ôl il…ô seΟß…ô bil…ôrsiniz.\n"
"\n"
"Τèg…ôr bu o q…ôd…ôr d…ô Οß…ôtin olmayan qaydalara …ôm…ôl ets…ôniz tez vaxtda mat ed…ô "
"bil…ôrsiniz:\n"
"    R…ôqibin ≈ûahΡ±nΡ± kΟΦnc…ô sΡ±xΡ±≈üdΡ±rmaΡüa c…ôhd edin.\n"
"<b>ΡΑzahat</b>: Bu halda r…ôqibin ≈ûahΡ±nΡ±n 8 gedi≈üi …ôv…ôzin…ô yalnΡ±z 3 gedi≈üi "
"olacaqdΡ±r.\n"
"    'Bir t…ôl…ô yaradΡ±n', ΟΕz piyadanΡ±zΡ± qurban verin.\n"
"<b>ΡΑzahat</b>: Bel…ôlikl…ô siz r…ôqibi ona …ôlveri≈üli olan yerd…ôn ΟßΡ±xara "
"bil…ôrsiniz.\n"
"    S…ôbirli olun.\n"
"<b>ΡΑzahat</b>: T…ôl…ôsm…ôyin. Fikirl…ô≈üin v…ô r…ôqibin nΟΕvb…ôti gedi≈üini hansΡ± "
"olacaΡüΡ±nΡ± tapmaΡüa ΟßalΡ±≈üΡ±n ki, onu …ôl…ô keΟßir…ô bil…ôsiniz v…ô ya da≈ülarΡ±nΡ±zΡ± "
