msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid ""
"Players take turns moving the seeds. On each turn, a player chooses one of "
"the six houses under their control. The player removes all seeds from that "
"house and distributes them, in a process called sowing, into the following "
"houses (counter-clockwise). Seeds are not distributed into the end scoring "
"houses, nor into the house drawn from. The starting house is always left "
"empty; if it contained 12 (or more) seeds, it is skipped, and the twelfth "
"seed is placed in the next house."
msgstr ""
"OyunΟßular nΟΕvb…ô il…ô toxumlarΡ± h…ôr…ôk…ôt etdirirl…ôr. Bir nΟΕvb…ôd…ô, bir oyunΟßu "
"n…ôzar…ôtind…ôki altΡ± evd…ôn birini seΟßir. OyunΟßu o evd…ôki bΟΦtΟΦn toxumlarΡ± "
"ΟßΡ±xarΡ±r v…ô …ôkir adlanan bir prosesd…ô h…ôr ev…ô saat yΟΕnΟΦnΟΦn …ôksin…ô bir d…ôn…ô "
"ataraq paylayΡ±r. Toxumlar n…ô son evl…ôr…ô, n…ô d…ô gΟΕtΟΦrΟΦl…ôn evl…ôr…ô paylanmΡ±r. "
"Ba≈ülanΡüΡ±c ev h…ômi≈ü…ô bo≈ü qalΡ±r; 12 (v…ô ya daha Οßox) toxum varsa, o, buraxΡ±lΡ±r "
"v…ô on ikinci toxum nΟΕvb…ôti ev…ô yerl…ô≈üdirilir."

#: activities/oware/ActivityInfo.qml:24
#: activities/oware_2players/ActivityInfo.qml:24
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid ""
"Capturing occurs only when a player brings the count of an opponent's house "
"to exactly two or three with the final seed he sowed in that turn. This "
"always captures the seeds in the corresponding house, and possibly more: if "
"the previous-to-last seed also brought an opponent's house to two or three, "
"these are captured as well, and so on until a house is reached which does "
"not contain two or three seeds or does not belong to the opponent. The "
"captured seeds are placed in the player's scoring house. However, if a move "
"would capture all of an opponent's seeds, the capture is forfeited since "
"this would prevent the opponent from continuing the game, and the seeds are "
"instead left on the board."
msgstr ""
"Toplama yalnΡ±z bir oyunΟßu r…ôqibin evinin sayΡ±nΡ± o nΟΕvb…ôd…ô …ôkdiyi son toxumla "
"tam iki v…ô ya ΟΦΟß…ô ΟßatdΡ±randa ba≈ü verir. Bu, h…ôr zaman uyΡüun evd…ôki toxumlarΡ± "
"v…ô b…ôlk…ô d…ô daha Οßoxunu toplayΡ±r: …ôg…ôr …ôvv…ôlki-sonuncu toxum da r…ôqibin "
"evini iki v…ô ya ΟΦΟß…ô ΟßatdΡ±rmΡ±≈üsa, bunlar da toplanΡ±r v…ô iki v…ô ya ΟΦΟß toxum "
"qalan v…ô ya r…ôqib…ô aid olmayan bir ev…ô Οßatana q…ôd…ôr bel…ô davam edir. "
"Toplanan toxumlar oyunΟßunun h…ôd…ôfl…ôdiyi ev…ô qoyulur. Ancaq bir h…ôr…ôk…ôtl…ô "
"r…ôqibin bΟΦtΟΦn toxumlarΡ± …ôl…ô keΟßiril…ôrs…ô, r…ôqibin oyuna davam etm…ôsin…ô mane "
"ola bil…ôc…ôyi ΟΦΟßΟΦn toplanmΡ±r v…ô toxumlar taxtada qalΡ±r."

#: activities/oware/ActivityInfo.qml:25
#: activities/oware_2players/ActivityInfo.qml:25
msgctxt "ActivityInfo|"
msgid ""
"If an opponent's houses are all empty, the current player must make a move "
"that gives the opponent seeds. If no such move is possible, the current "
"player captures all seeds in their own territory, ending the game."
